17:38.100 --> 17:41.321
♪ YOU'RE THE WAVE TO MY SEA

17:43.627 --> 17:46.195
♪ THE SUN AND MOON TO ME

17:48.806 --> 17:52.723
♪ YOU'RE THE WIND IN MY SAILS

17:54.073 --> 17:58.599
♪ RESCUE ME WHEN I FAIL

17:59.600 --> 18:03.082
♪ YOU'RE JUST WHAT I'M SEARCHING FOR

18:05.084 --> 18:08.478
♪ AND SO MUCH MORE

